[OVERLAY] VimFu — :s Captured Groups
[SAY] Capture groups let you rearrange matched text. Use escaped parentheses to capture, and backslash one through nine to refer to them.
[SAY] Swap first and last names. Capture each word, then reverse them.
[TYPE] ':%s/\\(\\w\\+\\) \\(\\w\\+\\)/\\2, \\1/'

